<section id="hero" class="relative">
  <div
    id="site-slogan"
    class="z-10 absolute top-16 w-full font-pjs font-medium text-[48px] tracking-[-3px] flex flex-col"
  >
    <span
      class="block uppercase text-sm md:text-base font-pjs text-accent font-extralight tracking-[-.5px] text-center md:relative md:-top-1"
      >Diseñamos a medida</span
    >
    <span
      class="leading-[2.8rem] md:leading-9 text-center text-[38px] md:text-5xl font-normal"
      >Tu felicidad,</span
    >
    <span class="leading-[1rem] text-center text-[38px] md:text-5xl font-normal"
      >nuestra meta.</span
    >
  </div>
  <div
    id="site-intro"
    class="absolute z-10 bottom-2 left-2 w-2/3 font-pjs font-light text-balance text-xl md:text-2xl text-accent leading-5 md:leading-6 tracking-tight"
  >
    Transformamos los espacios con la calidez y la belleza de la madera creando
    muebles y estructuras únicas.
  </div>
  <div id="video">
    <video
      autoplay
      loop
      muted
      playsinline
      class="lg:w-1/3 lg:relative lg:top-24 lg:left-[58%] "
    >
      <source src="/video/video-index.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
      Video no soportado
    </video>
    <div
      id="overlay"
      class="absolute lg:top-24 z-0 top-0 left-0 bg-gradient-hero w-full h-full lg:w-1/3 lg:left-[58%]"
    >
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<div id="cta" class="relative w-full lg:w-1/3 lg:left-[58%] ">
  <a
    href="#contacto"
    class="block bg-gradient-cta py-4 md:py-6 font-extrabold text-center text-dark uppercase text-xl md:text-2xl tracking-[-.6px] lg:rounded-b-xl"
    >Contactar</a
  >
</div>
